_source.title: PNET API - Errors
_source.description: Shows logs containing the one or more of the words "warning", "error", and "exception".

_source.title: PNET API - Logged HL7v2 Message
_source.description: Shows segments of the HL7v2 message that were logged.

_source.title: PNET API - Trace ID
_source.description: Shows logs which contain a Trace ID that is added as an HTTP Header in the API Gateway. This can be used to track messages between the API Gateway and PPM API.

_source.title: PNET API - Transaction UUID
_source.description: Shows logs that have the Transaction UUID field. This field can be used to track a single transaction's progress by adding a filter for the UUID value.
